<h2 id="features">Features</h2>

<p>Simples is packed with powerful features to showcase your content:</p>

<ul>
  <li>Beautiful, minimal design</li>
  <li>Single column post layout</li>
  <li>Responsive ‚Äì works perfectly on all devices</li>
  <li>Portfolio/projects post type to show your work</li>
  <li>Blog with pagination</li>
  <li>Sleek Ajax navigation and page transitions</li>
  <li>Unique ‚Äògallery‚Äô feature for image grids and carousels</li>
  <li>Full markdown support and code highlighting</li>
  <li>Social media icons</li>
  <li>Fast page rendering</li>
  <li>Built with SEO best practices in mind</li>
  <li>Customize everything ‚Äì colors, fonts, sizes etc. ‚Äì via a simple settings file</li>
  <li>Works with GitHub Pages</li>
  <li>Updated and supported by the developers</li>
</ul>

